data.description: This gorgeous home in the quiet community of Woodland Pines is exactly what you’ve been searching for. Nestled on a spacious lot, this property comes equipped with luxury vinyl plank flooring and a covered patio for outdoor entertaining and leisure. The kitchen comes equipped with granite countertops, tile backsplash, 42” cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. Find some peace and quiet in the private primary suite, complete with a tub and separate shower. Community comforts include a swimming pool and a park. Situated near Beltway 8 and I-69, residents will enjoy easy access to the Houston Ship Channel and Downtown Houston. Popular shopping, dining, and entertainment at Deerbrook Mall is just a short drive away! Schools are zoned to Humble ISD. Call today to book your private showing!
